put them in the background and

24
00:01:23.076 --> 00:01:27.109
continue to stay open to handle
incoming requests and things like that.

25
00:01:27.109 --> 00:01:32.104
That's why it's a very popular tool
because it kind of allows you to scale

26
00:01:32.104 --> 00:01:37.842
